name: Listen (carefully)
description:
Shhh......h Listen. Listen Carefully. Can you hear me? It doesn't have to be so quiet. Just Listen :)

This is one of works in my current project. It is talking about being a human. Being a human that is so blissful and also so hard, complicated and breakable. I'm trying my best to not be broken by creating these artwork. As a human. Staying alive together.
